Title: One with the Loa
Description:
Pieces of Lukou be scattered.

But her heart be deep inside the ogre mound.

De shadows can take us there. Quietly. Quickly. Speak to me when you are ready.
ObjectivesText: Talk to Kevo to be taken inside the Mosh'Ogg Ogre Mound.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Find Rokhan within the Mosh'Ogg Ogre Mound.
